children.text: Oh dear, you're dead, but don't despair!
You can buy a new tinderbox from the general store.
You can buy a new axe from Bob's Axe shop in south Lumbridge.
You can pick up a pickaxe above the gates of Lumbridge Castle or buy one from Bob's Axe shop in south Lumbridge.
You can get a new net from the Fishing Tutor in Lumbridge Swamps.
You can get new combat equipment from the combat tutors north of Lumbridge Castle.
You can buy a new hammer from the general store.
If you need more gold, kill goblins for a short while or try a quest.
Tutors can help you with skills and give you basic equipment. Look for this icon on your mini map.
More information is available in the manual on our website.
